name: New Rules
description:
The Admissions Committee has approved your admission as a student to Doughpe University. We are glad you plan to focus on your sense of style and fashion here with us. We believe as unit, we have what it takes to take you over the top in your own personal goals in fashion, and with your dedication you will be able to express your individuality to the best of your ability. As we grow, you grow. 

Congratulations on reaching this milestone and remember to “Stay Doughpe”
